dct_title_s: Farm land values, 1964, in dollars per acre
dct_description_sm: 2 maps on 1 sheet, Farm land values, 1964, in dollars per acre and Average size of farms, 1964, in acres. Computer generated isopleth maps obtained through use of the facilities of Indiana University's Research Computer Center.   ASCII-art maps created using SYMAP or similar technique.    Detached from: An atlas of Indiana / by Robert C. Kingsbury , with contributions from John M. Hollingsworth and others. Bloomington, Indiana : Department of Geography, Indiana University, [1970]. Page 61.
Imprint: Bloomington, Indiana : Department of Geography, Indiana University, [1970]
Scale: Approximately 1:3,000,000; Dimensions: each 26 x 10 cm, on sheet 28 x 21 cm
